  "code": "---\ntitle: MIP daemon\n---\nflowchart TB\n    Start((Start))\n    Init[Setup sockets, structures and accept connections]\n    Unsent[Send messages waiting for arp response]\n    Poll[Poll indefinitely]\n    ReadyFd{Which fd?}\n    RecvLower[Recieve from lower]\n    SendUpper[Send packet from upper]\n    RoutingUpper{Which routing type?}\n    RResponse[Send first packet waiting for rout]\n    ToBroadCast{Broadcast?}\n    Broadcast[Broadcast packet]\n    Forward{To me?}\n    IsArp{Arp?}\n    RecvArp[Store in cache, respond if request]\n    SendUp[Send up to the proper type]\n    Stored{Known interface+mac?}\n    SendArp[Send arp, store message]\n\n    Start --> Init --> Unsent --> Poll --> ReadyFd\n    ReadyFd-- Lower -->RecvLower --> IsArp\n        IsArp-- Yes -->RecvArp --> Unsent\n        IsArp-- No --> ToBroadCast\n    ReadyFd-- PING -->SendUpper\n    ReadyFd-- ROUTING -->RoutingUpper\n        RoutingUpper-- RESPONSE -->RResponse --> Unsent\n        RoutingUpper-- UPDATE -->SendUpper\n        RoutingUpper-- HELLO -->SendUpper\n    SendUpper --> ToBroadCast\n        ToBroadCast-- YES -->Broadcast -->Unsent\n        ToBroadCast-- NO -->Forward\n    Forward-- YES --> SendUp --> Unsent\n    Forward-- NO -->Stored\n        Stored-- YES -->Send --> Unsent\n        Stored-- NO -->SendArp --> Unsent\n",
